d\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"score\": 0.9880738603604343, \"rank\": 0.012070089195320073, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\"}, {\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9345196643693531, \"rank\": 0.07006843161252396, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999977774223, \"rank\": 2.2226838442359412e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Expectations are high, particularly for Thompson, who became this year's fastest man in the 100m after clocking a personal best of 9.77 seconds at the Jamaican Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9345196643693531, \"rank\": 0.07006843161252396, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9370921028119119, \"rank\": 0.06713096502056444, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, they will have to compete without 16-year-old sensation Bramwell.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\", \"score\": 0.9999999986919192, \"rank\": 6.447684085744966e-10, \"text\": \"Bramwell\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The teenager, who will miss his chance to debut at the Paris Olympics,gained recognition in May when he broke Bolt's Under-17 400m record at the 51st Carifta Games.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999977774223, \"rank\": 2.2226838442359412e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9982630205730649, \"rank\": 0.0017399989157724832, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bramwell narrowly beat Bolt's 22-year-old record of 47.33 seconds, set in 2002, with an impressive time of 47.26 seconds at the Kirani James Athletics Stadium in Grenada.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\", \"score\": 0.9999999986919192, \"rank\": 6.447684085744966e-10, \"text\": \"Bramwell\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\"}, {\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kirani\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirani\"}, {\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.8774320906458236, \"rank\": 0.11633963093480731, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}, {\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grenada\", \"score\": 0.9999999988694981, \"rank\": 1.1122910634608162e-09, \"text\": \"Grenada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grenada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grenada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon obliterating the long-standing record, the athlete said: \\\"It's a wonderful feeling to break the record.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since last summer, I have been eyeing the record, so it's a great feeling I could come out here and get it, I just took my mind off it and focused on the record.\\\"\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Defying belief, given Jamaica's reputation for producing fleet-footed stars, Bramwell openly shared with the Jamaican newspaper, the Gleaner, thatthere was a time he wasn't even the quickest in his class.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999999317879, \"rank\": 6.807956688372298e-11, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\", \"score\": 0.9999999986919192, \"rank\": 6.447684085744966e-10, \"text\": \"Bramwell\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bramwell_Booth\"}, {\"begin\": 1825, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9370921028119119, \"rank\": 0.06713096502056444, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During an exchange concerning his athletic inspiration, it is hardly surprising that Bolt emerged as his idol.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He further discussed how critical his family has been to both his personal life and burgeoning track career.\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"It's a great feeling, you know, to represent your country and to win for your country,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My family is always there.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are always at my track meets since the season has started.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not really answer that now about medals, but the season has been good.\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, I do not feel any pressure at all for this Championship really.\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a great feeling to represent Calabar.\\\"\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2763, \"end\": 2770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calabar_High_School\", \"score\": 0.9996222878348654, \"rank\": 0.00037602275467128943, \"text\": \"Calabar\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calabar_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calabar_High_School\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.323891224484147e-13, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 0.999999999